<p>
<lb n="1"/>naṁdanasaṁvatsarada māgha
<lb n="2"/>ba 30 sō sūryyagrahaṇa <unclear>ma</unclear>hā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>puṁṇyatithiyalu <unclear>ho</unclear>ṁnnava
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ttiya mahāprabhu hariya gau
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḍara saṁkkappagaḷa komā<unclear>ra</unclear> hiriya
<lb n="6"/>(hiriya) vīraṁṇaṁgaḷu cikkavīraṇna
<lb n="7" break="no"/>gaḷu gōnarājara Acarājaru sā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>vaṁṇa muṁtāda samasta <unclear>pra</unclear>jega
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḷu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> yalu Agastyagōtrada na
<lb n="10" break="no"/>vileya saṁkapa<unclear>ya</unclear>gaḷa maga ca
<lb n="11" break="no"/>Uḍappagaḷige dhāreyaṟadu koṭa
<lb n="12"/>vritti Ā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Āya <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="13"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> yaḍa
<lb n="14" break="no"/>keya <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> koṭa vritti <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> sarvvabādhāparihā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="15"/>kōṭi payāṁgavileymaṁ kōṭi tapōdhana <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="16"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kōṭiyaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="17"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> niṁtidanaḷidanu maṁ
<lb n="18" break="no"/>gaḷa mahāśrī śrī śrī
</p>

